sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C  as Caller / Service A
    participant G  as AXME Cloud API
    participant P  as Policy / State Store
    participant AU as Audit Trail
    participant O  as Observability

    C  ->> G:  create / controls / policy / resume / resolve
    G  ->> P:  mutate intent state or policy
    G  ->> O:  emit trace + metrics (trace_id, status, latency)

    alt policy mutation
        P  -->> G: policy_generation incremented
        G  ->> AU: action = policy_update\nold/new generation, patch summary
    else status mutation
        P  -->> G: status changed
        G  ->> AU: action = status_update\nold/new status, reason
    else write rejected
        P  -->> G: conflict or validation failure
        G  ->> AU: action = mutation_rejected, reason, actor
        G  ->> O:  emit error counter + latency
    end

    G  -->> C: API response + current generation / state
